_:Ndcdf9028e2d84b4495d99c1a0e8a51dd <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Deirdre Costigan was appointed Junior Lord of the Treasury (Government Whip) on 12 May 2026.</p>\n\n<p>She was previously Assistant Whip, House of Commons between 7 September 2025 and 12 May 2026. She was elected as the MP for Ealing Southall in July 2024.</p>\n" .
